gelayer-id\":\"k4k9865\"} --><p>Collaborating with SECURIVERSE was smooth and effective. Their expertise in email governance and adaptability to our needs made a significant impact. We\'ve noticed remarkable improvements in our email performance.</p><!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl_testimonial -->\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl_inner_col -->\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl_inner_col {\"overlay_hover_delay\":400,\"col\":4,\"pagelayer-id\":\"ddt5396\"} -->\n<!-- wp:pagelayer/pl_testimonial {\"image_position\":\"top-position\",\"alignment\":\"left\",\"author-spacing\":\"20\",\"avatar\":\"33\",\"testimonial_image_size\":100,\"img_shape\":\"circle\",\"cite\":\"Kristen Colen - Email Strategy Consultant\",\"cite_color\":\"#210d94ff\",\"cite_style\":\",20,,100,,none,,,,,\",\"designation\":\"Email Design Specialist\",\"designation_color\":\"#fb17ceff\",\"cite_designation_style\":\",16,,100,,,,,,,\",\"quote_content\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eFrom our first conversation to the final deployment, their professionalism and focus on our email needs were remarkable. They truly grasp the intricacies of email deliverability and offer smart, scalable solutions. We look forward to continuing our partnership!\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"ele_padding\":[\"20px\",\"20px\",\"20px\",\"20px\"],\"ele_bg_type\":\"color\",\"ele_bg_color\":\"#f5f9ffff\",\"cite_spacing\":[\"10\",0,\"10\",0],\"testimonial_border_type\":\"dotted\",\"testimonial_border_color\":\"#210d94ff\",\"testimonial_border_width\":[\"3\",\"3\",\"3\",\"3\"],\"border_radius\":[\"20px\",\"20px\",\"20px\",\"20px\"],\"pagelayer-id\":\"xmm6378\"} --><p>From our first conversation to the final deployment, their professionalism and focus on our email needs were remarkable. They truly grasp the intricacies of email deliverability and offer smart, scalable solutions. We look forward to continuing our partnership!</p><!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl_testimonial -->\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl_inner_col -->\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl_inner_row -->\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl_col -->\n<!-- /wp:pagelayer/pl_row